Revision history for Tickit-Widget-Choice

0.06    2021-11-20
        [CHANGES]
         * Updates for Object::Pad 0.57
            + Use :isa instead of legacy `extends`
            + Use ADJUSTPARAMS instead of ADJUST

0.05    2021-07-03
        [CHANGES]
         * Update to Object::Pad 0.41:
            + Use :param to simplyify BUILD block

0.04    2020-06-13
        [CHANGES]
         * Update to Object::Pad 0.27
            + BUILD block syntax
            + package+class declaration to keep metadata parsers happy

0.03    2020-03-27
        [CHANGES]
         * Use Object::Pad

0.02    [BUGFIXES]
         * Set WIDGET_PEN_FROM_STYLE to keep Tickit 0.50 happy (RT103397)

0.01    2014/12/02 00:04:11
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

